## рџ“ќ Notes

> Detection is URI-based only (GET/query-string parameters) вЂ” POST body payloads are not currently inspected.
>
> Signature set is defined as a single `pattern` constant (`xss_patterns`) and is extendable via `&redef`.
>
> Feeds into Wazuh via a custom decoder/rule for centralized alerting.

